cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.AI 

The paper focuses on building a voice-only interface for a movie recommender system, which involves natural language processing and human-computer interaction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL) techniques. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for recommendation (cs.AI) and the evaluation of the system's performance (cs.SD).
